@DualTechTechnicalTest_HostAddress = http://localhost:5008

### Get All Clients
GET {{DualTechTechnicalTest_HostAddress}}/api/Clients/getAll
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Client by ID
GET {{DualTechTechnicalTest_HostAddress}}/api/Clients/getById/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create New Client
POST {{DualTechTechnicalTest_HostAddress}}/api/Clients/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "name": "John Doe",
  "identity": "12345678A"
}

###

### Update Existing Client
PUT {{DualTechTechnicalTest_HostAddress}}/api/Clients/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "John Smith",
  "identity": "12345678A"
}

